      "content": "A modest square of packed earth ringed by low stone buildings with slate roofs. A stone well stands in the centre, its rope descending into darkness. Smoke drifts from a chimney to the east where a tavern sign swings on rusted chains. To the west, a gap between the houses opens onto dunes and the sound of surf."
    },
