      "content": "The low-ceilinged room is warm and dim, lit by tallow candles guttering in glass jars. A long bar of driftwood planks runs along the far wall, its surface stained dark with years of spilled ale. A matchbox has been left on the bar. A trapdoor in the floor leads down to a cellar."
